Power Query Editor - View - Preview  



Transform vs Add column in power query editor


transform work with existing column
Add column make the transformation in a new column and keeps the original column




Filtering or “slicering” data in the power query editor preserves the data. In the model view of the report then it doesn’t preserve the filtering. Only in the power query editor

This is a permanent change that will be register into the steps - unlike filtring in an excel sheet for example


