Keeping and removing rows after sorting:



Merge vs append queries: 




Merging queries:


Check join kind
Merge queries expand the table horizontally (might be exception with outer joins etc)
Where as append queries expand the table vertically (usually the column names are the same - think of it more like a union in tableau)
Merge add columns – append add rows


Can merge as new or  just merge queries only




Unhiding hidden tables



